25:08.473 --> 25:11.375
I'm looking for Jay Moore.

25:11.410 --> 25:12.684
I don't think he's here.

25:12.719 --> 25:13.850
I mean, he's not here.

25:13.885 --> 25:15.412
They're separated.

25:15.447 --> 25:17.051
Oh.

25:17.086 --> 25:19.284
Big fight.

25:19.319 --> 25:20.758
Yeah?

25:20.793 --> 25:21.418
Huge.

25:25.325 --> 25:28.095
You know, this is
really not necessary.

25:28.130 --> 25:29.932
Well, you don't
want to watch me eat.

25:32.673 --> 25:33.529
OK.

25:33.564 --> 25:36.037
Well, thank you.

25:36.072 --> 25:37.368
So what can you tell
me about this fight?

25:37.403 --> 25:38.710
Were you over there?

25:38.745 --> 25:40.646
Uh, no, no, no, here.

25:40.681 --> 25:42.373
I don't know.

25:42.408 --> 25:45.750
I guess sound must carry at
night, but they were just--

25:45.785 --> 25:47.213
man, they were
really going at it.

25:47.248 --> 25:48.819
Do they fight a lot?

25:48.854 --> 25:50.821
More so lately.

25:50.856 --> 25:53.725
Oh, did Maggie file
a restraining order?

25:53.760 --> 25:55.320
Is that why you're here?

25:55.355 --> 25:57.729
Can't say.

25:57.764 --> 26:01.293
But maybe did you hear
anything specific about what

26:01.328 --> 26:02.635
they were fighting about?

26:02.670 --> 26:06.298
I mean, it was
pretty garbled, but she

26:06.333 --> 26:08.069
did yell the word "filth."

26:08.104 --> 26:10.401
I caught that.

26:10.436 --> 26:11.644
Filth.

26:11.679 --> 26:13.910
And then he was banished.

26:13.945 --> 26:16.110
He did come back one
day to work on the lawn,

26:16.145 --> 26:17.683
and that did not go over well.

26:17.718 --> 26:19.476
[coughing]

26:19.511 --> 26:20.444
Oh, no.

26:20.479 --> 26:21.313
Was there too much pepper?

26:21.348 --> 26:22.017
Wow.

26:22.052 --> 26:22.952
You want milk?

26:22.987 --> 26:23.986
I'm fine.
I'm fine.

26:24.021 --> 26:24.954
Please, please, please sit.

26:24.989 --> 26:25.988
I'm fine.

26:26.023 --> 26:27.957
