29:30.042 --> 29:31.371
He fucking killed her.

29:31.406 --> 29:32.273
Who's this?

29:32.308 --> 29:33.307
Jay?

29:33.342 --> 29:34.946
Chief of police was just here.

29:34.981 --> 29:36.046
Jesus fucking Christ.

29:36.081 --> 29:37.278
They're going to
nail me for this.

29:37.313 --> 29:38.807
You understand?

29:38.842 --> 29:40.644
That's what's up, dude,
but you know, there's still

29:40.679 --> 29:42.811
the matter of my finder's fee.

29:42.846 --> 29:44.285
What?

29:44.320 --> 29:45.682
What did you just say?

29:45.717 --> 29:47.519
I mean, look, I
get things went awry.

29:47.554 --> 29:48.289
But--

29:48.324 --> 29:49.862
Things went awry?

29:49.897 --> 29:53.965
