29:59.533 --> 30:00.631
Fuck you!

30:00.666 --> 30:01.467
[banging]

30:01.502 --> 30:02.039
Fuck you!

30:02.074 --> 30:02.908
Fuck you!

30:02.943 --> 30:03.535
Fuck!

30:12.711 --> 30:13.611
Piece of shit phone.

30:22.259 --> 30:24.589
