even if the potato chips or what

30:24.624 --> 30:26.558
have you are cheaper
somewhere else, that they have

30:26.593 --> 30:28.934
to buy Castle Subs products?

30:28.969 --> 30:30.595
JERRY CONNORS (ON PHONE):
That's right, officer.

30:30.630 --> 30:31.827
OK, got it.

30:31.862 --> 30:33.400
Thank you for your
time, Mr. Connors.

30:33.435 --> 30:34.731
JERRY CONNORS (ON
PHONE): My pleasure.

30:37.076 --> 30:39.538
Well, Jay Moore
is into something.

30:39.573 --> 30:42.079
Because he's selling
shitty no name chips?

30:42.114 --> 30:44.609
It's a breach of the
franchise agreement.

30:44.644 --> 30:47.117
He has to buy
Castle Subs product.

30:47.152 --> 30:49.581
If he buys from Liberty
Bell foods or wherever else,

30:49.616 --> 30:51.583
he stiffs corporate
out of their money.

30:51.618 --> 30:53.882
Either way, what's that got
to do with his murdered wife?

30:53.917 --> 30:55.389
I do not know.

30:55.424 --> 30:57.061
Because you seem really
worked up over this.

30:57.096 --> 30:59.888
Well, we have a victim who
was unable to yield any clues

30:59.923 --> 31:01.395
due to her--

31:01.430 --> 31:03.463
Crispiness.

31:03.498 --> 31:04.134
Christ's sakes.

31:04.169 --> 31:05.762
KB, will you--

31:05.797 --> 31:08.270
Sorry, it just happens.

31:08.305 --> 31:10.041
Don't do it anymore.

31:10.076 --> 31:12.571
What do you got?

31:12.606 --> 31:14.738
Called all the
transport companies.

31:14.773 --> 31:16.311
No one had a pickup
near the B Line.

31:16.346 --> 31:19.644
Also Jay's story checks
out at the diner.

31:19.679 --> 31:22.086
Also there's a record of
his call to Maggie's cell,

31:22.121 --> 31:24.055
just like he told you.

31:24.090 --> 31:25.122
So we've got nothing.

31:27.918 --> 31:29.995
Hey, two Maggie Moores guy.

31:30.030 --> 31:31.997
[bell]

31:33.429 --> 31:34.758
Uh, what?

31:34.793 --> 31:36.430
Two Maggie Moores
in the system, one

31:36.465 --> 31:38.465
at 32 Hanover,
you guys on Donna.

31:38.500 --> 31:39.268
Remember?

31:39.303 --> 31:40.467
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

31:40.502 --> 31:42.766
Dude, what a
crazy coincidence.

31:42.801 --> 31:45.307
[scoffs] What are
the odds of that?

31:49.115 --> 31:51.511
Mr. Moore.

31:51.546 --> 31:53.678
Mr. Moore.

31:53.713 --> 31:54.646
Mr. Moore.

31:54.681 --> 31:56.351
[bell]

31:56.386 --> 31:58.089
Yeah.

31:58.124 --> 32:01.323
Yeah, let me get a mega bowl
and a couple of those phones.

32:10.631 --> 32:14.204
No, it was weird for me to see
my name in a story like that.

32:14.239 --> 32:16.206
Mags, you seen my glasses?

32:16.241 --> 32:18.538
In here!

32:18.573 --> 32:20.045
Well, tell Daddy that I'm fine.

32:20.080 --> 32:22.806
It was just one of those
spooky coincidences, OK?

32:22.841 --> 32:24.478
So I'll see you on Tuesday, Mom.

32:24.513 --> 32:26.447
OK, I love you, too.

32:26.482 --> 32:28.152
OK, bye.

32:28.187 --> 32:30.022
Your folks OK?

32:30.057 --> 32:32.057
Yeah, I talked them down.

32:32.092 --> 32:35.060
[music playing]

33:42.085 --> 33:43.293
Hey, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!

33:43.328 --> 33:43.887
